<item>
            <title>[LU-11044] ext4_dir_operations uses iterate_shared() in Linux 4.7</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11044</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Linux 4.7 commit ae05327a00fd47c34dfe25294b359a3f3fef96e8 replaces&#160;ext4_dir_operations iterate with iterate_shared. dir_relaxed_shared()&#160;was also added in that commit, so we can use that function to verify&#160;that the ext4_dir_operations is using iterate_shared.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/torvalds/linux/commit/ae05327a00fd47c34dfe25294b359a3f3fef96e8&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/torvalds/linux/commit/ae05327a00fd47c34dfe25294b359a3f3fef96e8&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
